            image:       'https://techcrunch.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/c.ai-Series-1.jpg',
            url:         'https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/09/character-ai-enters-the-microdrama-arena-with-its-own-productions-but-with-a-twist/',
